item.title: Heellpp! me please
item.dc:creator: @jordan7 Jordan7
item.description:
@jordan7 wrote:

Ok here is the pic…

Ok now exit the archive then open up your folder. You should see Compile, right click it and click edit. Remove everything there and add this code…

@echo off title Compiler "%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause

Then save it, exit and right click runserver and click edit.

Remove everything that is there and place this code…

@echo off title Runserver set java="C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\java.exe" java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server pause

There they now both work. To run your server I usually go to compiler and press r then enter, it should say running server on 0.0.0. or something then 5555 or 43594 whatever your port is. Then open up moparscape look at your hamachi ip at top enter that and your port and you can log in…

PM me if you need more help or ask here. Thank You,

-Jordan7
